@host = http://localhost:5297

### ── 1. CSV Format Upload ──────────────────────────
POST {{host}}/api/deliveries/upload/csv
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----BoundaryCSV

------BoundaryCSV
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

OrderId,Customer,Address,DeliveryDate,Weight
ORD-10001,Almacenes Generales,Avenida de la Constitucion 45,2099-06-15,125.50
ORD-10002,Distribuidora Norte,Calle Industrial Sur 12,2099-07-20,45.20
------BoundaryCSV--


### ── 2. TXT Format Upload (Pipe-Delimited, No Header) ─
POST {{host}}/api/deliveries/upload/txt
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----BoundaryTXT

------BoundaryTXT
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

ORD-20001|Transportes Gomez|Avenida Siempreviva 742|20990815|85.40
ORD-20002|Servicios Logisticos|Calle Falsa 123|20990920|110.15
------BoundaryTXT--


### ── 3. JSON Format Upload ─────────────────────────
POST {{host}}/api/deliveries/upload/json
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----BoundaryJSON

------BoundaryJSON
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.json"
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "shipmentNumber": "ORD-30001",
    "recipient": "Supermercados El Barrio",
    "destination": "Plaza Mayor 10",
    "scheduledDate": "2099-10-10T00:00:00Z",
    "packageWeight": 250.75
  },
  {
    "shipmentNumber": "ORD-30002",
    "recipient": "Ferreteria Central",
    "destination": "Callejón del Grano 5",
    "scheduledDate": "2099-11-15T00:00:00Z",
    "packageWeight": 15.30
  }
]
------BoundaryJSON--


### ── 4. XML Format Upload ──────────────────────────
POST {{host}}/api/deliveries/upload/xml
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----BoundaryXML

------BoundaryXML
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.xml"
Content-Type: application/xml

<Deliveries>
  <Delivery>
    <Code>ORD-40001</Code>
    <ClientName>Farmacia San Jose</ClientName>
    <Location>Avenida Libertad 500</Location>
    <Date>2099-12-05</Date>
    <Kg>5.80</Kg>
  </Delivery>
  <Delivery>
    <Code>ORD-40002</Code>
    <ClientName>Importaciones Mundiales</ClientName>
    <Location>Muelle Comercial 8</Location>
    <Date>2099-12-20</Date>
    <Kg>1250.00</Kg>
  </Delivery>
</Deliveries>
------BoundaryXML--


### ── 5. Cross-Format Validation Error (JSON Route, CSV File) ──
POST {{host}}/api/deliveries/upload/json
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----BoundaryError

------BoundaryError
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="mismatch_data.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

OrderId,Customer,Address,DeliveryDate,Weight
ORD-99999,Invalid CrossFormat,Calle Falsa,2099-01-01,10.0
------BoundaryError--
